OL,3,CMan appears in court after Bristol
OL,4,Cshooting
OL,6,FA 24-year-old man has appeared in
OL,7,Fcourt following a shooting in Bristol
OL,8,Fthat left a man in his 20s seriously
OL,9,Finjured.
OL,11,FWilliam Scammell, 24, from Speedwell,
OL,12,Fappeared before Bristol Magistrates'
OL,13,FCourt on Saturday (4 April) charged
OL,14,Fwith attempted murder and being in
OL,15,Fpossession of a shortened shotgun.
OL,17,FAvon and Somerset Police launched a
OL,18,Fmanhunt after a gun was fired at a car
OL,19,Fon Speedwell Road at around 1.50pm on
OL,20,FWednesday 1 April.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
