OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1775555970
OL,3,CMan appears in court after Bristol
OL,4,Cshooting
OL,6,FThe victim, a man in his twenties,
OL,7,Fremains in hospital with serious
OL,8,Finjuries.
OL,10,FScammell is due to appear before
OL,11,FBristol Crown Court on 13 May.
OL,13,FAnother man and a woman, also both in
OL,14,Ftheir 20s, were arrested on suspicion
OL,15,Fof assisting an offender after the
OL,16,Fincident. They have since been
OL,17,Freleased on police bail.
